aa(lp178
V"The Joy of Voting" project isn't just about joy.
p179
aVIt's about this passion.
p180
aVIt's about feeling and belief,
p181
aVand it isn't just our organization's work.
p182
aVAll across this country right now,
p183
aVimmigrants, young people, veterans, people of all different backgrounds
p184
aVare coming together to create this kind of passionate, joyful activity
p185
aVaround elections,
p186
aVin red and blue states, in urban and rural communities,
