VImagine where this country would be
p242
aVif all the folks who in 2010 created the Tea Party
p243
aVhad decided that, you know, politics is too messy,
p244
aVvoting is too complicated.
p245
aVThere is no possibility of our votes adding up to anything.
p246
aVThey didn't preemptively silence themselves.
p247
aVThey showed up,
p248
aVand in the course of showing up, they changed American politics.
